INSTALATION
-----------

I guess that if you are reading this you already downloaded and extracted
the files from the tarball :)

So what's next...

  * Install the plugin
  * Install the css
  * Create links
  * Copy images
  
 
INSTALLATION STEPS

1) Copy the doku directory into the wordpress plugins directory

   cp -R /path/to/doku /path/to/wordpress/wp-content/plugins

2) Append the doku css to the wordpress theme's css.

   cat /path/to/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/doku/doku-style.css >>
       /path/to/wordpress/wp-content/themes/current-theme/style.css

3) Create the links to the smilies and images directories

   cd /path/to/wordpress
   ln -s /path/to/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/doku/smileys .
   ln -s /path/to/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/doku/media .

4) copy all images in doku/images to /path/to/wordpress/wp-content/themes/current-theme/images/

That's it!
Enjoy the power of the dokuwiki Markup

